2.caption: 2022 NFL Pro Bowl
2.description: The 2022 Pro Bowl will be the National Football League all-star game for the 2021 NFL season. It is scheduled to be played at Allegiant Stadium in Las Vegas, Nevada on February 6, 2022. ESPN, ABC and Disney XD have the national television rights. Voting for the game started on November 16. The entire roster will be announced in December.
2.inspected:Announcers: Steve Levy, Brian Griese, Louis Riddick and Lisa Salters
